Subject: MDM settings?
Description: Hello We are using an MDM solution (Mosyle) for our MAC workstations to set system permissions for applications. Is there a support document available that lists all of the permission and settings that need to be set when using Endpoint Protector on macOS devices? I found this document (https://www.endpointprotector.com/support/pdf/manual/Endpoint_Protector_5_JAMF_Deployment_User_Manual_5209_EN.pdf) but note sure if this is still applicable with later versions of Endpoint Protector. I appreciate your help.
What_We_Know__c: We have provided the link to our latest JAMF deployment guide.
Next_Steps__c: We are waiting for the customer's feedback
Solution_Comment__c: The customer requested the latest documentation for JAMF deployment, and we have provided the link to it on our documentation site https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EndpointProtector_5.9.4/page/Content/EndpointProtector/Install/Agent/JAMF/Overview.htm
